[
  {
    "filename": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-63686436.pdf_57.pdf",
    "page_index": 57,
    "core_content": {
      "parsing_res_list": [
        {
          "block_label": "paragraph_title",
          "block_content": "大红袍",
          "block_bbox": [
            140,
            230,
            436,
            353
          ],
          "block_id": 0,
          "block_order": 1
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "武夷岩茶有“茶中之王”的美誉，为中国名茶之，其中红袍是武夷岩茶中的极品，享誉全球。\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            632,
            269,
            1918,
            374
          ],
          "block_id": 1,
          "block_order": 2
        },
        {
          "block_label": "paragraph_title",
          "block_content": "历史传说",
          "block_bbox": [
            135,
            2270,
            331,
            2316
          ],
          "block_id": 2,
          "block_order": 3
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "武夷岩茶历史悠久，而大红袍乃是武夷岩茶中的佼佼者。大红袍之所以特别引人关注，首先在于它的稀贵。历史上的大红袍，本来就少，而如今公认的大红袍茶树，仅是九龙窠岩壁上的那几棵。\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            114,
            2367,
            943,
            2636
          ],
          "block_id": 3,
          "block_order": 4
        },
        {
          "block_label": "image",
          "block_content": "外形茶汤叶底\n紧结壮实，稍扭曲，色泽汤色深橙黄，香气浓长，软亮匀齐\n油润滋味醇厚，岩韵明显\n\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            58,
            466,
            1916,
            1468
          ],
          "block_id": 4,
          "block_order": null
        },
        {
          "block_label": "vision_footnote",
          "block_content": "产区福建武夷山。",
          "block_bbox": [
            93,
            1534,
            451,
            1585
          ],
          "block_id": 5,
          "block_order": null
        },
        {
          "block_label": "image",
          "block_content": "福建省\n\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            308,
            1691,
            713,
            2203
          ],
          "block_id": 6,
          "block_order": null
        },
        {
          "block_label": "paragraph_title",
          "block_content": "保健功效",
          "block_bbox": [
            1052,
            1543,
            1261,
            1592
          ],
          "block_id": 7,
          "block_order": 5
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "强心解挛：大红袍中的咖啡碱具有强心、解痉、松弛平滑肌的功效，能解除支气管痉挛，促进血液循环。\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            1027,
            1644,
            1883,
            1807
          ],
          "block_id": 8,
          "block_order": 6
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "抗菌抑菌：大红袍中的茶多酚和酸作用于细菌，能凝固细菌的蛋白质，将细菌杀死。",
          "block_bbox": [
            1025,
            1851,
            1880,
            1954
          ],
          "block_id": 9,
          "block_order": 7
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "最佳品饮时节春夏时节。",
          "block_bbox": [
            1045,
            2021,
            1555,
            2067
          ],
          "block_id": 10,
          "block_order": 8
        },
        {
          "block_label": "paragraph_title",
          "block_content": "储藏方法",
          "block_bbox": [
            1046,
            2147,
            1255,
            2194
          ],
          "block_id": 11,
          "block_order": 9
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "大红袍保存时最好不要使用玻璃罐、瓷罐、木盒或药罐，因为这些器具具有透光、不防潮、易碎的缺点。最好先用小罐子分装少量茶叶，以便随时取用，其余的茶叶则用大罐子密封起来储存在冰箱里保存。\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            1022,
            2232,
            1877,
            2515
          ],
          "block_id": 12,
          "block_order": 10
        },
        {
          "block_label": "paragraph_title",
          "block_content": "适合人群",
          "block_bbox": [
            1043,
            2598,
            1251,
            2645
          ],
          "block_id": 13,
          "block_order": 11
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "一般人群皆可饮用，儿童、孕妇不适宜饮用。",
          "block_bbox": [
            1025,
            2684,
            1821,
            2729
          ],
          "block_id": 14,
          "block_order": 12
        },
        {
          "block_label": "number",
          "block_content": "50",
          "block_bbox": [
            121,
            2768,
            169,
            2804
          ],
          "block_id": 15,
          "block_order": null
        }
      ],
